{"tid":1772110,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"128 和勇同行 和理港島 勇武九龍","createTime":"2019-12-06T10:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T15:35:58.000Z","uid":24178,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20e051c871d1d966cf6580cc9cbe397d7fb34248","tid":1772110,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"港島地勢險要 極難退場 <br />\n除時引發難民潮 實在唔太適合開波<br />\n希望手足安全為上<br />\n現提議勇武手足可以係九龍開花<br />\n就算出港島都請做足功課及盡量輕裝<br />\n<br />\n港島由和理非頂<br />\n和理非食TG唔會死<br />\n勇武拉一個就少一個<br />\n<br />\n不分化係不會因為手法不同而分化<br />\n但今次因為安全先至提議咁做<br />\n<br />\n不同意既留低意見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保護勇武<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分咩春128 一齊出港島"},{"pid":"8e2e9d01dd6edce25412975f462914170ea81a1c","tid":1772110,"uid":72943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"真係咁分咪重狗九龍一拉拉晒<br />\n<br />\n自由發揮啦"},{"pid":"6c50955bdbd5a7660ad137114ed40363f9173284","tid":1772110,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"勇武各區<br />\n和理非港島"},{"pid":"d4f27d36a4a4231b524e3fb36ab10abe905a8c9d","tid":1772110,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac5a46c632aa993c6969fe4ab5ce159e84ad4f0","tid":1772110,"uid":105873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}